{"tid":1931121,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[1118理大]鄺手足還押119日後准予保釋","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T05:27:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8158245b3cc72f2682965d5626509499fdca48","tid":1931121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:02:00.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀署理主任裁判官 <br />\n#保釋覆核<br />\n<br />\n鄺<br />\n<br />\n控罪：暴動 (違反公安條例 第19條)<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2019年11月18日，在九龍漆咸道南與暢運道交界，與其他不知名人士一起參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n另涉於9月8日維園非法集結及管有士巴拿被捕<br />\n<br />\n裁判官准予被控人保釋：<br />\n擔保金： 40,000<br />\n宵禁： 21至07<br />\n禁足： 公主道、梳士巴利道及漆咸道南<br />\n每星期報到3次<br />\n居住於報稱地址<br />\n交出所有旅遊證件<br />\n不得離港<br />\n<br />\n3月24日於西九龍裁判法院第三庭聆訊"},{"pid":"a1d23032a6acfdc244e6f98f113926e1d33a8107","tid":1931121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012ed0b52f6bc537191ad28658562f5c4871ab4b","tid":1931121,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"食屎狗官,無證據坐咗百幾日冤獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5617cf68db7d3c10fb1f0f0522f44abd8fe434ba","tid":1931121,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"012ed0b52f6bc537191ad28658562f5c4871ab4b","tid":1931121,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"食屎狗官,無證據